                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On April 16, Secretary Acheson testified before the Senate Foreign Relations
                    Committee that the threat of famine in India was immediate, and he urged passage
                    of S. 872, the bill before the committee. See the text of the Secretary’s
                    statement in Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, April 23,
                    1951, page 674.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
